          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-1" n="1">Now hardly here and there an hackney Coach</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-2" n="2">Appearing, show'd the Ruddy Morn's Approach.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-3" n="3">Now Betty from her Master's Bed had flown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-4" n="4">And softly stole to discompose her own.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-5" n="5">The slip-shod 'Prentice from his Master's door,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-6" n="6">Had par'd the Dirt, &amp; sprinkl'd round the Floor.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-7" n="7">Now Moll had whirl'd her Mop w<hi rend="superscript">tḥ</hi> dextrous Airs,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-8" n="8">Prepar'd to Scrub the Entry and the Stairs.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-9" n="9">The Youth with Broomy Stumps began to Trace</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-10" n="10">The kennell-Edge, where Wheels had worn the Place.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-11" n="11">The Small-Coal-Man whas heard with Cadence deep,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-12" n="12">'Till drown'd in Shriller Notes of Chimney-Sweep:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-13" n="13">Duns at his Lordship's Gate began to Meet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-14" n="14">And Brick-dust Moll had Scream'd thrô half a Street.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-15" n="15">The Turnkey now his Flock retuning sees,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-16" n="16">Duely Let out a-Nights to Steal for Fees.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-17" n="17">The Watchfull Bailiffs take their silent Stands,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-124-002D-line-18" n="18">And School-Boys Lag with Satchels in their hands.</l>
          </lg>
